so-style-type:personal;\r\n\tfont-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";\r\n\tcolor:#1F497D;}\r\nspan.EmailStyle21\r\n\t{mso-style-type:personal-compose;\r\n\tfont-family:"Arial","sans-serif";}\r\n.MsoChpDefault\r\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\r\n\tfont-size:10.0pt;}\r\n@page WordSection1\r\n\t{size:8.5in 11.0in;\r\n\tmargin:1.0in 1.0in 1.0in 1.0in;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n\t{page:WordSection1;}\r\n--></style><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:shapedefaults v:ext="edit" spidmax="1026" />\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:shapelayout v:ext="edit">\r\n<o:idmap v:ext="edit" data="1" />\r\n</o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]--></head><body lang=EN-US link=blue vlink=purple><div class=WordSection1><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Hello Dave -<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Glad you liked the audio! Here''s a short bio:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>---<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Victor David Sandiego was the winner of the 1st WordStorm Poetry Competition held on Vancouver Island in British Columbia, a winner of the 2008 Jeanne Lohmann Poetry Prize, and the winner of the 2009 Crab Creek Review poetry contest. His work appears in various journals and on public radio. He lives in the high desert of central México. For more, see: www.VictorDavid.com.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>---</span><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif"''><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Also, the piece that you accepted, Teeth in My Hands, is part of a larger work. I''d appreciate it if you can mention that. For example:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-size:14.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Teeth in My Hands<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>From: <i>The Second Book of Muwadi</i><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";color:#984807''>(text)</span><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Or after the text if that works better for your formatting. Thanks again!! And please let me know if you need more info.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Victor David Sandiego <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span style=''font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText>From: qarrtsiluni [mailto:qarrtsiluni@gmail.com] <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Sent: Wednesday, August 24, 2011 8:09 PM<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>To: Victor David Sandiego<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Subject: Re: 3 poems<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Hi Victor,<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Great reading! Thanks. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>If we can view that Submishmash profile, I''m not aware of it. If you could just paste the bio into an email, that''d be great. Thanks.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Dave<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>On Mon, Aug 22, 2011 at 12:45 PM, Victor David Sandiego &lt;vds@victordavid.com&gt; wrote:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Hello Dave &#8211;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Thanks much for the acceptance. I look forward to seeing the various works in the upcoming issue.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>A recording (in .wav format, about 5 MB) is here:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>http://media.victordavid.com/wav/<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Please let me know if you need more information.&nbsp; I&#8217;m not sure if you can view my Submishmash profile bio or if I should supply it separately.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Thanks again.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Victor David Sandiego <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>From: Qarrtsiluni [mailto:qarrtsiluni=gmail.com@submishmash.com] On Behalf Of qarrtsiluni<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Sent: Wednesday, August 10, 2011 2:14 PM<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>To: Victor David Sandiego<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Subject: RE: 3 poems<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Hi Victor, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Congratulations on the acceptance! I''m writing to encourage you to try making an audio recording for our daily podcast. Please see our page on how to go about it: <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>http://qarrtsiluni.com/how-to-contribute/how-to-make-an-audio-recording/ <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>I can record you by phone, if necessary--let me know and we''ll figure out a time when I can call. Hope to hear from you soon. If we can get a recording within the next month, that''d be great. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Best, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Dave Bonta <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Managing Editor <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>http://qarrtsiluni.com <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>You are receiving this email because you have an account with a publisher or organization that uses Submishmash. If you''d like to unsubscribe and stop receiving all notification emails from Submishmash organizations, please CLICK HERE TO UNSUBSCRIBE.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Error! Filename not specified.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>-- <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Beth Adams and Dave Bonta<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Managing Editors, qarrtsiluni<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>http://qarrtsiluni.com<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText>Submissions are open for the Worship issue, edited by Fiona Robyn and Kaspalita. Now playing: the Imprisonment issue. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoPlainText><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p></div></body></html>');
