div style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:13px"><strong>If you are informing us that your work has been accepted elsewhere</strong>, congratulations and thank you for letting us know.\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:13px">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:13px">Responses have been sent to all those who entered the\r\n<strong>Lyric Essay Contest</strong>,<strong> </strong>and the results are now posted at\r\n<a href="http://lumfa.blogspot.com/2013/11/lyric-essay-contest-results.html">http://lumfa.blogspot.com/2013/11/lyric-essay-contest-results.html</a>.\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:13px">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:13px">If you have a question, we will reply as soon as possible.&nbsp;Questions can also be emailed&nbsp;directly to the Editor at\r\n<a href="mailto:bmead@lindenwood.edu">bmead@lindenwood.edu</a>. &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:13px">\r\n<div><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><i>The Lindenwood Review&nbsp;</i></div>\r\n<div>www.lindenwood.edu/lindenwoodReview&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>LUmfa.blogspot.com</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>');
