o:idmap v:ext="edit" data="1" />\r\n</o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]--></head><body lang=EN-US link=blue vlink=purple><div class=WordSection1><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Dear Leslee of The MOON Magazine &#8211;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Going with option #2 on your submissions guidelines page, I&#8217;ll take a chance and email a submission for your consideration. I think the following pieces might be in alignment with your current theme of &#8220;Spiritual Politics&#8221;.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>&#8226;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; They Kill The Fat Ones<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>&#8226;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Portrait Of Her Unfinished History<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>&#8226;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Retribution Befriends My Enemy<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>However you interpret these pieces, thanks for taking a look. I appreciate the opportunity to share these with you. And happy anniversary to MOON also.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Victor David Sandiego<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>99Poets@VictorDavid.com<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>p.s. Your guidelines don&#8217;t mention whether to send an attachment or not. Obviously, as you&#8217;ve seen by now, I&#8217;ve attached a PDF file. Hope that&#8217;s okay.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>');
