></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:black''>Victor David<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><div><div style=''border:none;border-top:solid #B5C4DF 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0in 0in 0in''><p class=MsoNormal><b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"''>From:</span></b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"''> Leslee Goodman [mailto:leslee@moonmagazine.org] <br><b>Sent:</b> Friday, December 20, 2013 12:48 PM<br><b>To:</b> ''Victor D. Sandiego''<br><b>Subject:</b> RE: Submissions to The MOON Magazine<o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''color:#1F497D''>Hi Victor,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''color:#1F497D''>Thank you for writing!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''color:#1F497D''>I do like your third piece a great deal &#8220;Retribution Befriends My Enemy, or How the Assassination Backfired.&#8221;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''color:#1F497D''>Can you send it to me as a Word or text document please, along with a bio and a head shot\x3f<br>Thank you so much for sharing your work with The MOON!<br>Leslee<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><a name="_MailEndCompose"></a><span style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><div><div style=''border:none;border-top:solid #B5C4DF 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0in 0in 0in''><p class=MsoNormal><b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"''>From:</span></b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"''> Victor D. Sandiego <a href="mailto:[mailto:99poets@VictorDavid.com]">[mailto:99poets@VictorDavid.com]</a> <br><b>Sent:</b> Friday, December 20, 2013 8:34 AM<br><b>To:</b> <a href="mailto:leslee@moonmagazine.org">leslee@moonmagazine.org</a><br><b>Subject:</b> Submissions to The MOON Magazine<o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Dear Leslee of The MOON Magazine &#8211;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Going with option #2 on your submissions guidelines page, I&#8217;ll take a chance and email a submission for your consideration. I think the following pieces might be in alignment with your current theme of &#8220;Spiritual Politics&#8221;.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>&#8226;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; They Kill The Fat Ones<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>&#8226;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Portrait Of Her Unfinished History<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>&#8226;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Retribution Befriends My Enemy<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>However you interpret these pieces, thanks for taking a look. I appreciate the opportunity to share these with you. And happy anniversary to MOON also.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>Victor David Sandiego<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><a href="mailto:99Poets@VictorDavid.com">99Poets@VictorDavid.com</a><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";color:black''>p.s. Your guidelines don&#8217;t mention whether to send an attachment or not. Obviously, as you&#8217;ve seen by now, I&#8217;ve attached a PDF file. Hope that&#8217;s okay.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>');
