t;; font-size: 10pt;"><FONT face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></DIV><FONT face="Times New Roman" size="3">\r\n\r\n</FONT><DIV><SPAN lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">(If\r\nyou are interested in re-submitting to ditch, in the future, we usually ask\r\nwriters to wait about a year between submissions.)</SPAN></DIV><FONT face="Times New Roman" size="3">\r\n\r\n</FONT><DIV><SPAN lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"><FONT face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></DIV><FONT face="Times New Roman" size="3">\r\n\r\n</FONT><DIV><SPAN lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">So,\r\nwelcome to ditch, !!</SPAN></DIV><FONT face="Times New Roman" size="3">\r\n\r\n</FONT><DIV><SPAN lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">Thanks,\r\nJohn</SPAN></DIV><FONT face="Times New Roman" size="3">\r\n\r\n</FONT><BR><BR>--- 99poets@VictorDavid.com wrote:<BR><BR>From: "Victor D. Sandiego" &lt;99poets@VictorDavid.com&gt;<BR>To: &lt;ditch@ditchpoetry.com&gt;<BR>Subject: Submission<BR>Date: Sat, 14 Dec 2013 18:59:52 -0600<BR><BR><DIV><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">December 14, 2013</SPAN></P></DIV><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P></DIV><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">Dear Editors of Ditch Poetry –</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">The attached document contains the following pieces for your consideration:</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; His Unprotected Desire</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Elephant Death Of War</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The One Act Play of Man</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Stubborn Complacency Of Our Vision</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Signposts</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">as well as a brief bio. As requested, a headshot photo (about 76 kb) is also attached.</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">Thanks for taking a look.</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">Sincerely,</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;