an style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:black''><a href="http://www.subprimal.com"><span style=''color:blue''>www.subprimal.com</span></a><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:black''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"''>From:</span></b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"''> ditch@ditchpoetry.com [mailto:ditch@ditchpoetry.com] <br><b>Sent:</b> Monday, January 13, 2014 3:51 PM<br><b>To:</b> Victor D. Sandiego<br><b>Subject:</b> Editor''s Choice<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><div><div><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>Hi, just thought I would let you know that I greatly admire your work and added your profile to the Editor''s Choice page of ditch, : <a href="http://www.ditchpoetry.com/editorschoice.htm">http://www.ditchpoetry.com/editorschoice.htm</a><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"''>thanks, John<o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div></div></body></html>');
