 site for me\x3f</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">Thanks for your support. I was excited to find Ditch as an outlet experimental work and am having fun going through the archives.</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><SPAN style="color: rgb(99, 36, 35); font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;">Victor David</SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;"><A href="http://www.victordavid.com"><SPAN style="color: blue;">www.victordavid.com</SPAN></A></SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;"><A href="http://www.subprimal.com"><SPAN style="color: blue;">www.subprimal.com</SPAN></A></SPAN></P><P><SPAN style="color: black; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P><B><SPAN style="font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">From:</SPAN></B><SPAN style="font-family: &quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;"> ditch@ditchpoetry.com [mailto:ditch@ditchpoetry.com] <BR><B>Sent:</B> Monday, January 13, 2014 3:51 PM<BR><B>To:</B> Victor D. Sandiego<BR><B>Subject:</B> Editor''s Choice</SPAN></P><P>&nbsp;<DIV></DIV><DIV><DIV></DIV></DIV></P><P><SPAN style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">Hi, just thought I would let you know that I greatly admire your work and added your profile to the Editor''s Choice page of ditch, : <A href="http://www.ditchpoetry.com/editorschoice.htm">http://www.ditchpoetry.com/editorschoice.htm</A></SPAN><DIV></DIV></P><P><SPAN style="font-family: &quot;