"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">If you would like to subscribe or order individual issues &#8211; subscriptions and sales are vital for the on-going existence of\r\n<i>Flash</i> &#8211; please go to: <a href="http://www.chester.ac.uk/flash.magazine/subscriptions">\r\nhttp://www.chester.ac.uk/flash.magazine/subscriptions</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">With thanks and best wishes,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Ashley Chantler and Peter Blair<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><i><span style="font-size:12.0pt">Flash: The International Short-Short Story Magazine</span></i><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><a href="http://www.chester.ac.uk/flash.magazine"><span style="color:blue">http://www.chester.ac.uk/flash.magazine</span></a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">***<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="border:none;border-top:solid #B5C4DF 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">From:</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"> Victor D. Sandiego [mailto:99poets@VictorDavid.com]\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Sent:</b> 20 February 2014 01:34<br>\r\n<b>To:</b> flashmagazine<br>\r\n<b>Subject:</b> Submissions to Flash: The International Short-Short Story Magazine<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Dear Editors of Flash &#8211;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">The attached documents contain the following pieces for your consideration:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><![if !supportLists]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">A New World Every Five Minutes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><![if !supportLists]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Eternal Custodians Of Chains<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><![if !supportLists]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Portrait Of Her Unfinished History<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><![if !supportLists]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">The Third Descent Of Angels<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Per your guidelines, these are not currently under consideration elsewhere.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">While investigating a possible home for these pieces, I came across another publication of flash that included a link to your web site.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Thanks for taking a look. I appreciate the opportunity to share these with you.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Victor David Sandiego<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#595959">attached:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#595959">Flash_Victor_David_Sandiego_A_New_World_Every_Five_Minutes_2014-02-19.docx<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#595959">Flash_Victor_David_Sandiego_Eternal_Custodians_Of_Chains_2014-02-19.docx<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n