hould you feel inclined to extend your support even more, we have UK, European and International Subscription options too. \r\n<br />\r\n<br />Just visit this link: http://barefictionmagazine.co.uk/buy-it/\r\n<br />\r\n<br />Thanks again Victor David and don''t forget that sharing is just as welcome.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />Here are some handy links for you:\r\n<br />Magazine: http://www.barefictionmagazine.co.uk\r\n<br />Facebook: http://facebook.com/BareFiction\r\n<br />Twitter: http://twitter.com/BareFiction\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />Yours,\r\n<br />Robert Harper\r\n<br />Editor\r\n<br />Bare Fiction Magazine\r\n<br />\r\n<br />http://barefictionmagazine.co.uk/\r\n<br />\r\n<br />"It''s the words that count" \r\n<br />\r\n<br />Registered with Duotrope: https://duotrope.com/market_13297.aspx <img width="1px" height="1px" alt="" src="http://email.email.submittable.com/o/ZD1kN2Q1OSZpPTIwMTQwODMwMTUyMDMwLjUyMjk5Ljk0NTk2JTQwZW1haWwuc3VibWl0dGFibGUuY29tJmg9ZDM2OTNkZWE2ZmY4OGRiM2JkNDRmYzQ5ZTk2OGUyNGMmcj05OXBvZXRzJTQwdmljdG9yZGF2aWQuY29t">');
INSERT INTO "submission_message" ("id", "entry_id", "submissionbatchid", "outgoing", "sender_name", "sender_email", "recipient_name", "recipient_email", "subject", "display", "sent_date", "received_date", "body_format", "body") VALUES (255, E'000000009A53EC4398D3BF48BB7911BF7EA7F5EE44E92C00', 321, E'0', E'Eleven Eleven', E'hughsteinberg@yahoo.com', E'99poets@victordavid.com', E'99poets@victordavid.com', E'Your submission to Eleven Eleven', E'Your submission to Eleven Eleven', '2014-08-31 18:00:22', '2014-08-31 18:00:30', 1, E'Dear Victor David Sandiego:\r\n\r\nThank you so much for sending us your writing. We all read it closely, and it sparked much discussion among the staff, where it made its way past our initial screening of submissions.\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, it didn''t work within the context of this issue of the journal, but we hope that you will feel encouraged by this short note to send us something else.\r\n\r\nOur next print issue will be published in August 2014. We''ll begin reading for our winter online issue, #18, in September 2014.\r\n\r\nWarmly,\r\nThe Eleven Eleven Staff\r\n\r\n2014-08-31 15:59:56 (GMT -7:00)');
