e he writes, studies, and plays drums with jazz combos and in musical / poetry collaborations. His work appears  in various journals (Cerise Press, Crab Creek Review, Floating Bridge Review, Off The Coast, Generations Literary Journal, Poetry Salzburg Review, The Tishman Review, others) and has been featured on public radio. He is the founder and current editor of Subprimal Poetry Art. His website is victordavid.com.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:#0D0D0D''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:green''>2. Payment information - whether you would like to be paid by check or<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:green''>by paypal, and to what address the payment should be sent.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:#0D0D0D''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:#0D0D0D''>PayPal please, email for PP is: paypal@victordavid.com<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:#0D0D0D''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:green''>3. Optional: an mp3 recording of the poem. We would love to receive it<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:green''>within the next two weeks, but longer is a possibility.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:#0D0D0D''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Verdana","sans-serif";color:#0D0D0D''>I will make a recording in 