he opportunity to read your work which you emailed to us recently.  Unfortunately, we are unable to use it.</font></span></p><p style="margin:0in 0in 0pt;line-height:26px;text-indent:0.5in">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif">Please excuse any delay in our response.  We try to read and report back within six to eight weeks on all the work we receive, but on occasion the volume of manuscripts—hard copies and emailed attachments—sent to our office keeps us from meeting this schedule. </span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="margin:0in 0in 0pt;line-height:26px;text-indent:0.5in"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif">Thanks for your interest in our magazine.  We are sorry we cannot comment on work individually because of the demands of our editorial and production duties.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin:0in 0in 0pt;line-height:26px;text-indent:0.5in"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif"><br></span></p><p style="margin:0in 0in 0pt;line-height:26px;text-indent:0.5in">\r\n<span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif">                                                                                           The Editors</span><b style="line-height:normal"><font face="Cambria"> </font></b></p>\r\n\r\n<div style="border-bottom-color:black;border-width:medium medium 2.25pt;border-style:none none solid;padding:0in 0in 1pt"><p style="margin:0in 0in 0pt;border:medium none;padding:0in"><b><font face="Cambria"> </font></b></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="margin:0in 0in 0pt;border:medium none;padding:0in"><br></p></div></div></div>\r\n<br></div>\r\n<br></div>\r\n<br></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><div class="gmail_quote">On Fri, Aug 26, 2016 at 1:23 PM, Victor D. Sandiego <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:99poets@victordavid.com" target="_blank">99poets@victordavid.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex"><div lang="EN-US" link="blue" vlink="purple"><div class="m_6810485479012838513WordSection1"><p class="MsoNormal">Dear Editors of Confrontation –<u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">The attached document contains the following pieces for your consideration:<u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="m_6810485479012838513MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:.5in"><u></u><span style="font-family:Symbol"><span>·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><u></u>Confrontation (425 words)<u></u><u></u></p><p class="m_6810485479012838513MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:.5in"><u></u><span style="font-family:Symbol"><span>·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><u></u>The Hidden Beaches (273 words)<u></u><u></u></p><p class="m_6810485479012838513MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:.5in"><u></u><span style="font-family:Symbol"><span>·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><u></u>Boss Seems Fed Up (429 words)<u></u><u></u></p><p class="m_6810485479012838513MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:.5in"><u></u><span style="font-family:Symbol"><span>·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><u></u>Big Tujunga (221 words)<u></u><u></u></p><p class="m_6810485479012838513MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:.5in"><u></u><span style="font-family:Symbol"><span>·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><u></u>Hospital Games (247 words)<u></u><u></u></p><p class="m_6810485479012838513MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:.5in"><u></u><span style="font-family:Symbol"><span>·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><u></u>Nature of Things (145 words)<u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Thanks for taking a look. I appreciate the opportunity to share these with you.<u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX">Sincerely,<u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX">Victor D. Sandiego<u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX">A.P. 170 Centro<u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX">36001 Guanajuato, Gto.<u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX">Mexico<u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES-MX"><u></u> <u></u></span></p></div></div></blockquote></div><br></div>');
